Information Collection and Use

Task Manager for iOS does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data.

The app operates entirely on your device. All system metrics — including CPU usage, memory, GPU utilization, disk storage, network activity, and battery health — are read locally using standard iOS system APIs and are never sent to any external server.




