Third-Party Services

Task Manager for iOS does not integrate any third-party services, SDKs, or analytics tools. The app has no network communication of its own.




Data Storage

All data displayed in the app exists only in your device's temporary memory while the app is running. No data is written to disk or persisted after the app is closed.




Children's Privacy

Our app does not collect any personal information from anyone, including children under the age of 13. The app is safe for users of all ages.




